{"id":646754,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/人物日志｜新闻联播是检验事实存在的唯一标准/","date":"2020-06-10T02:13:57Z","modified":"2020-06-10T02:13:57Z","title":"人物日志｜新闻联播是检验事实存在的唯一标准","content":"<p>微友：昨晚在父母家吃饭，新闻联播刚完父子俩就吵起来了，原因是儿子把广西水灾刷屏的视频给父亲看，父亲说中央新闻联播没播，苦劝儿子不要相信谣言……</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646755\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"843\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646756\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"728\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646757\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"652\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646758\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"588\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/4.png 273w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/4-255x300.png 255w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646759\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"629\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/5.png 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/5-238x300.png 238w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646760\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/6.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/6-138x300.png 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/6-473x1024.png 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/6-768x1664.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/6-709x1536.png 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/6-945x2048.png 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>媒体存在的意义是客观真实的报道所发生的事情</p>\n<p>据说：数省暴雨成灾，52条河流超过警戒，主流媒体统一装聋作哑，是家丑不可外扬？</p>\n<p>对人类最大的伤害，一是不受限制的权利，二就是天灾！</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-646761 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"228\" height=\"303\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/7.png 228w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/7-226x300.png 226w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 228px) 100vw, 228px\" /></p>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,38912,38985],"tags":[9273,9006,9013]}